data.description: This BEAUTIFUL home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, over 2700 square feet and is located on one of the most sought-after streets in Chelsea Park!  As you enter, you will be captivated by soaring vaulted ceilings, a beautiful hardwood staircase with wrought-iron railings, and an abundance of natural light. Enjoy the convenience of a main-level master suite with a soaking tub and separate shower. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a HUGE island for entertaining, ample cabinet space, granite countertops and upgraded stainless-steel appliances. Upstairs, you will find a loft area with 3 additional bedrooms and another full bath. You will also love the huge backyard with its' gorgeous view!  Community amenities include an in-ground pool, walking trails, two lakes and an award-winning elementary school. Convenient to shopping, dining, and only 30 minutes from downtown Birmingham!  Schedule your showing TODAY!
